OL,3,CArrests after north Belfast stabbing
OL,5,FTwo men have been arrested after two
OL,6,Fmen were stabbed in north Belfast
OL,7,Fovernight.
OL,9,FPolice were called to a report of an
OL,10,Faltercation in the Cambrai Street area
OL,11,Fat around 3am on Saturday.
OL,13,FThey located two men at the scene with
OL,14,Fstab wounds.
OL,16,FThe men were taken to hospital for
OL,17,Ftreatment on injuries not believed to
OL,18,Fbe life-threatening.
