OL,3,CArrests after north Belfast stabbing
OL,5,FA man in his 20s and a man in his 30s
OL,6,Fwere arrested on suspicion of wounding
OL,7,Fwith intent and possession of bladed
OL,8,Farticle.
OL,10,FThey remain in custody at this time,
OL,11,Fassisting with police enquiries.
